name: Cypher Hybrid
description:
This piece talks about the origin of human knowledge, and its cosmic nature. Believing to be coincidental, humans live their lives comparing themselves to other forms of carbon-based life, not realizing that what they call intelligence comes from a strictly human perspective. Some might say that, in a drop of water in the ocean, there can be entire civilizations of self-conscious bacteria.

All assets including soundtrack are original and made by Psybonacci.
If you collect this, reach me out on twitter, i can send you the full lenght song. It's a demo song called "D22".
Dimensions: 1000x1000 px
Lenght: 38s
Framerate: 14,286 fps
Audio: 44100 kHz | 128kbps
